dc_title_s: Rutgers College of Agriculture and Environmental Science, New Jersey 1973
dc_creator_sm: Rutgers University Department of Physical Plant
dc_description_s: Map of the Rutgers University College of Agriculture and Environmental Science occupying the present day Douglass Campus. Includes building directory. Map includes portion of campus in New Brunswick borough and the outlying departments in North Brunswick Township including the Rutgers Gardens property and the horticulture farms.
